fg_segments: Your privacy is important to us. To better protect your privacy we provide this statement explaining our Privacy Policiy and the choices you can make about the way your information is collected and used. Personal Information:
The personal information collected are your name, country, email address and browser information.
We use that information strictly internally to provide you with a better service.
COLOR CLIMAX does not sell or share your personal information with any outside company.
Credit Card Information: We use CCBill and Epoch's third-party credit card processing services.
The credit card information that you provide during the registrations process are directly submitted to the credit card companies and are not stored on our servers for security reasons.
The signup pages are secure and encrypted with the latest security technologies.
Cookies: When you visit colorclimax.com, we send one or more cookies to your browser.
We use cookies to improve the quality of our service and to determine if the user is logged in as a member or not.
These cookies do not contain any private information and can not be traced back to you as a user.
Email Advertisement: When we release a new service, or offer a limited-time membership discount, we may send you a promotional email to inform you of these new services.
Please note that this only applies to prior existing customers of the COLOR CLIMAX Website.
Our Commitment To Data Security: To protect your information and to prevent the unauthorized access to our servers, we continuously apply the latest security and encryption technologies.
If you have any questions or concerns, you can contact our Legal Department directly at: legal@colorclimax.com
As a 40-year old company, we value the loyalty and respect the privacy of our customers. COLOR CLIMAX Corporation, Denmark

Your privacy is important to us. To better protect your privacy we provide this statement explaining our Privacy Policiy and the choices you can make about the way your information is collected and used.
Personal Information:

                        The personal information collected are your name, country, email address and browser information. We use that information strictly internally to provide you with a better service.
                    
COLOR CLIMAX does not sell or share your personal information with any outside company.
Credit Card Information:
We use CCBill and Epoch’s third-party credit card processing services. The credit card information that you provide during the registrations process are directly submitted to the credit card companies and are not stored on our servers for security reasons. The signup pages are secure and encrypted with the latest security technologies.
Cookies:
When you visit colorclimax.com, we send one or more cookies to your browser. We use cookies to improve the quality of our service and to determine if the user is logged in as a member or not. These cookies do not contain any private information and can not be traced back to you as a user.
Email Advertisement:
When we release a new service, or offer a limited-time membership discount, we may send you a promotional email to inform you of these new services. Please note that this only applies to prior existing customers of the COLOR CLIMAX Website.
Our Commitment To Data Security:
To protect your information and to prevent the unauthorized access to our servers, we continuously apply the latest security and encryption technologies. If you have any questions or concerns, you can contact our Legal Department directly at: legal@colorclimax.com
                        


As a 40-year old company, we value the loyalty and respect the privacy of our customers. 
COLOR CLIMAX Corporation, Denmark
